### vim: ft=ratpoison fde fdm=marker fmr=#<,#> fdc=3 fdl=1:
#< ${HOME}/etc/ratpoisonrc
#   ‗‗‗‗‗‗‗‗‗‗‗‗ ‗‗‗‗‗‗ ‗‗‗‗‗‗‗‗ ‗‗‗‗‗‗‗‗‗‗‗
